	<longTexts>
		<longText name="ksm_Help_1">
<![CDATA[This Script varies the steering speed, the steering back speed and the maximum steering angle  depending on the current vehicle speed.
In addition the camera is rotated according to the steering angle an the driving direction. The digital accelerator (keys a and w) can be limited.
Only when Shift-Left is pressed at the same time 100% acceleration or braking happens.
If the acceleration limiter is set to 100% then acceleration and braking are limited when Shift-Left is used.

All functions can be switched off.]]>
		</longText>
